PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of MANDEEP (ROSHI) K. CHADHA of Westmount, Quebec, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the National Gallery of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Rhoda Kokiapik.
